text: The Grand Duchy of Moscow, Muscovite Russia, Muscovite Rus' or Grand Principality of Moscow (; or Muscovy in English from the Latin )Introduction into the Latin epigraphy (Введение в латинскую эпиграфику) . was a principality in Rus'. It was in the late Middle Ages in Moscow. It was before Tsardom of Russia which was made in the early modern period. It was ruled by the Rurik dynasty. ==References== Category:History of Russia Category:Former countries in Europe
title: Grand Duchy of Moscow
